== Demographics ==
According to the 1991 Bangladesh census, Kapasia had a population of 303,710, of whom 154,204 were aged 18 or over. Males constituted 50.83% of the population, and females 49.17%. Kapasia has an average literacy rate of 37% (7+ years), against the national average of 32.4%.<ref name="census">{{Cite web}}</ref>

